Quickstrike:





Quickstrike snickered and watched Scorponok. "Ah like t' see 'im 
try," he mumbled under his mouth plate. "Sheilds, on-line." he 
ordered the computer. The shields came on as he commanded. "Now t' 
an' blow yerself up, tin-horn." He chuckled, shaking his shoulders. 
The strips at his cheeks briefly quivered. 

He turned his head to Vemonous. "Ah gotta get t' th' command room. Ya 
stay here an' watch that scorpion-bot. Tell me if he gets rowdy." He 
bolted from the monitoring room, down to the bridge. 

He opened his comm-link to Black Arachnia. "Hate t' disturb yer 
beauty sleep, sugar-bot, but we's got Scorponok right outside. Ah'm 
givin' 'im th' Inferno right now!"
